Articles.Content: When I try to place engines they unplace them self and the node I used dissapears, I'm on the latest 1.6 update with the dlc

I assume RO means Realism Overhaul here.

There is no 1.6.1 version of Realism Overhaul, and the DLC is not supported by RO, thus you can expect all sorts of problems with installing RO in ksp version 1.6.1

The most recent version that RO is compatible with is 1.4.5, but it works much better in 1.3.1
